  -- tên weyâlen krêkidot ::

* zîl :: nominal :: some Martian drug more dangerous than cocaine or heroin :: 

* maimis :: adjective :: mad, crazy
  - maimisunth :: nominal :: madness, insanity
  - î maimisunth tepsôdh !! :: IS madness you-DATIVE

* -unth :: nominalizing adjectival suffix :: -ness 

* strab :: verbal :: to stand, to "take a stand", to exist

* kolt :: nominal :: matter, affair
  - hûn tortâlen qâthoteps koltîz-tik ::

* feletain :: nominal :: the royal court (of a Jagarôth city)
  - vê panâlen tepsot feletainîz !! ::
  - I will see you in the royal court!!!
  - FUTURE see-FINITE-1s 2spronoun-ACCUSATIVE court of law-LOCATIVE

* qâth :: nominal :: mind, sensorium, a sapient's lived experience of the world 
  - hûn tortâlen qâthoteps koltîz-tik ::
